Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美麗的夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認真跳起的舞蹈\N將會替這個夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染上多麼美麗的顏色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說呢？舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:02:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～原來妳是HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然偽裝成男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第20話 炎之舞 淚之命運\N這種卑鄙的手法還不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第20話 炎之舞 淚之命運\N閉嘴!妳為什麼找上巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷看起來很痛對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上真的痛死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，害我受傷的就是他姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…妳應該懂吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源內，出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧隱之術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把那女孩\N轉到正派經營的醫院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，正經事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾斯的宣傳四課
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就所謂諜報部門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們跟我聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說想交易情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追殺妳弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有假裝成男生的HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽巧海是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼…開始進行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，還不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撥的號碼是0…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聯絡不上舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跑來通知我這個導師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有種不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，幫我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這件事怎辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要讓妳和玖我夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚐嚐跟這傷一樣的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!我求妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最寶貝的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是很討厭他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡面是不是認為\N要是沒有這個弟弟就好了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沈醉在努力的姊姊這個角色中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳總是把她當作手下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不就當作小鬼看待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，狩獵行動就從現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的說謊姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著，拜託妳，住…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病房遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好像失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽她一定很擔心吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛…\N又發燒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不舒服就早點睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨，就去恨妳姊姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖，煩人的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，快!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝恩情!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沈重…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳其實是很討厭他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡面是不是認為\N要是沒有這個弟弟就好了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經答應過媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，你聽好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖在這裡等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跑進河裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丟下巧海一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海失蹤了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可以坐在這裡發呆呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，妳自己呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳至今是為了什麼而戰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回想起來啊，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前突然出現的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧正從月杜追蹤巧海他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了，夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，這裡剛才已經走過了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶，到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個是結城同學對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說姊姊害她受傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我想我非知道不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老姊也是HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她拼命想阻止\NHiME之間互鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為HiME一旦被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該HiME所最重視的人就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，如果我被擊敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或許…就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會對你這個這麼軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點男子氣概都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很溫柔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是跟晶在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳才讓我想要繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會乞求原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望妳們能獲得神的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要迷惑她們，以便將之攔下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之子會吸收被打倒的\N對手的力量而變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過舞衣她的力量太過強大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓她失去最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後靠結城收拾\N叫不出心之子的舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N就可以消除最大的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓妳成為最強的HiME\N來拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想要這種東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜之王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會取代你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的力量是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要找舞衣麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，現在不可以回宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去禮堂避難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留!\N夏姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在磨蹭什麼，快點下車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，妳振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是充滿榮譽的執行部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰要來守護\N學校的風紀與"技安"啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳總算恢復平常的狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走，雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城，借一下雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老在同樣地方打轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了，巧海他有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點!好像有什麼黑影在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守住你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃!源內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人，怎麼可以這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不…起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是妳下手的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳把巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把晶…打倒了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以舞衣才生氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是沒辦法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖，那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能來得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是無論如何都該避免掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？不該是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣妳太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的是最棒的舞者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣攻擊我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊過來的對象都是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…舞衣是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人就非得打倒不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法完全遮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點避難!不要拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了，快點動作!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們知道自己在幹什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾久崎晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是舞衣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳說過最喜歡的人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞…衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這種感情很棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳總算打倒我這個老頭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命小姐\N妳除了兄長黑曜之王之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能喜歡其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳成長得非常出色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是個正格的公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手把最喜歡的老爹給…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一個人看的很重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有多難受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本就不懂!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不曾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心喜歡過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著，不可以攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的忘記你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊真正想要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什麼也沒有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就換那個人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一切都是假象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該已經察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷戀一個人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!我哪有戀愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:23:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色君王 ， 覺醒之刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪!大事不妙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現一家非常好吃的蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是少女的一件重要大事\N非去不可呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們這麼輕鬆，真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姊姊知道我寫了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了預防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是先寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊就跟媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有姊姊在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我真的很感謝姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種話語
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.43,0:24:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本完全無法表達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
