Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.33,0:24:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不要難過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我真的很幸福
